(1) build the docker image

docker build -t my-apache2 .


(2) run the image

docker run -p 80:80 -dit --name my-app my-apache2

(3)

access address http://localhost or http://127.0.0.1


(4) to check what is running

docker ps -a

(5) To stop and remove the container

docker stop my-app
docker rm my-app